## **1. Root Configuration Files**

### `/Users/ujjwalraj/Developer/revio/package.json`
```json
{
  "name": "revio",
  "private": true,
  "scripts": {
    "build": "turbo run build",
    "dev": "turbo run dev",
    "lint": "turbo run lint"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "turbo": "^2.5.0"
  },
  "packageManager": "pnpm@10.30.0"
}
```

### `/Users/ujjwalraj/Developer/revio/pnpm-workspace.yaml`
```yaml
packages:
  - "apps/*"
  - "packages/*"
```

### `/Users/ujjwalraj/Developer/revio/turbo.json`
```json
{
  "$schema": "https://turbo.build/schema.json",
  "tasks": {
    "build": {
      "dependsOn": ["^build"],
      "outputs": ["dist/**", ".next/**", "!.next/cache/**"]
    },
    "dev": {
      "cache": false,
      "persistent": true
    },
    "lint": {
      "dependsOn": ["^build"]
    },
    "generate": {
      "cache": false
    },
    "test": {
      "dependsOn": ["^build"],
      "outputs": ["coverage/**"],
      "cache": false
    },
    "type-check": {
      "dependsOn": ["^build"],
      "cache": true
    }
  }
}
```

